That Tamia Dance
.
.
.
.
.
For the first time in at least 10 years I went back to my alma mater for homecoming. It has changed drastically since I was there including the @ukblackalumni_fubutailgate. It was amazing to see black alumni and current students gather in one place to catch a vibe. For those of my classmates who weren’t able to attend I advise you put it on the calendar for next year. 
Sidebar: I thought it would be cool to catch this line dance from above 🤷🏾‍♂️
